        <p>
          <b>Fixes</b>
        </p>
        <ul id="ul_9A00A9B41407480A806F613401CB9C03">
          <li id="li_780C405A312A4805A5D6240EC1B807EE">
            <!--AN-92678, AN-100543-->Fixed
				a discrepancy between Reports &amp; Analytics and data warehouse data by adding
				support for 
				<term>campaign instances</term> as a segmentation metric to data
				warehouse. 
			 </li>
          <li id="li_6A3C4F5A87724F80A79A5E4BF5900D5A">
            <!--AN-97671-->Fixed an
				issue with data warehouse requests with Mobile App ID. 
